and challenging what defines the best VR player.\u2028Today, we are proud to launch a new version customized for Quest series. With a wide range of advanced features, Moon VR transforms your headset into an immersive theater. But don't let its sophistication deter you\u2014 it also comes with a simple and intuitive interface.\n\nKey features:\nMultiple modes supported and automatically recognized: 180\u00b0/ 360\u00b0/ 2D/ 3D\nMultiple formats supported: mkv/ mp4/ wmv/ mov/ avi/ rmvb/ flv\nMultiple subtitles and audio tracks supported\nRemove faulty ghosting in videos\nHead tracking and effortless hands-free control\nMoon Link: wirelessly watch VR videos from your computer\nScreen adjustments: Brightness, distance, zoom, and curved display\nRotate, mirror and single-eye viewing\nBackground environments: galaxy, sea view and more to be released\nAdvanced antialiasing to smooth shaking\n\nChill and Enjoy!", "short_description": "Stream and watch the best VR videos for FREE! Moon VR can also stream virtual reality videos from your PC."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://moonvrplayer.com/privacy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "InnoVision", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://moonvrplayer.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "434961926215971"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["PRODUCTIVITY", "UTILITY", "MEDIA_PLAYER"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id"